text.tspan: Per capita CO₂ emissions in 2016 vs 1990
Per capita emissions of carbon dioxide (CO₂) in the year 2016 versus 1990 emissions. Countries which lie above the
grey line had higher per capita emissions in 2016 than in 1990; countries below the line had lower per capita
Source: OWID based on Global Carbon Project (GCP) and UN Population data
